---
title: Spiced Chicken & Bechamel Leek Sauce with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Chicken, mash and steamed veggies, it sure has the essence of home cooking at it’s finest. A leek sauce for seared chicken is just the thing this classic dish needs to make it five star home cooking.

*Unfortunately, this
week's baby broccoli
was in short supply, so
we've replaced it with
silverbeet. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just
as delicious, just be
sure to follow your
recipe card!*
